<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 01:18:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币兄弟似乎在逃避向美国国税局报告销售情况</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-14/crypto-bros-appear-to-be-dodging-reporting-sales-to-the-irs</link><description>一份新报告表明，很多人可能没有向美国国税局报告加密货币持有情况。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iXcegfz3ZNQ4/v15/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-14/crypto-bros-appear-to-be-dodging-reporting-sales-to-the-irs</guid></item><item><title>在伊朗乐观情绪中，比特币测试交易区间的高端</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/bitcoin-climbs-to-four-week-high-on-hopes-of-us-iran-peace-talks</link><description>由于对美国可以与伊朗达成协议以结束冲突的乐观情绪，风险资产上涨，比特币趋向两个多月交易区间的高端。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCYQ_y689Ysc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 01:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/bitcoin-climbs-to-four-week-high-on-hopes-of-us-iran-peace-talks</guid></item><item><title>德意志交易所以 2 亿美元入股加密货币交易所 Kraken</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/deutsche-borse-takes-200-million-stake-in-crypto-exchange-kraken</link><description>德意志交易所股份公司 (Deutsche Börse AG) 向加密货币交易平台 Kraken 的母公司 Payward Inc. 投资了 2 亿美元，这家法兰克福证券交易所运营商开始通过区块链轨道提供更广泛的证券交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iC3VHIX_kBFo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 09:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/deutsche-borse-takes-200-million-stake-in-crypto-exchange-kraken</guid></item><item><title>Kraken 加密货币交易所称犯罪团伙声称有权访问部分客户数据</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/kraken-says-criminal-group-claims-access-to-some-customer-data</link><description>Kraken 是世界上最古老的加密货币交易所之一，该交易所表示，它正受到一个声称有权访问某些客户账户信息的犯罪集团的勒索。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iL9LUVY0OPx8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 20:15:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/kraken-says-criminal-group-claims-access-to-some-customer-data</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 通过混合证券购买 10 亿美元比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/strategy-funds-entire-1-billion-bitcoin-buy-with-hybrid-securities</link><description>自 7 月推出高收益证券以来，Michael Saylor&amp;#39;s Strategy Inc. 首次完全通过出售其“Stretch”永久优先股为其最新每周 10 亿美元的比特币购买提供资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8fRz00ApIV0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 14:37:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/strategy-funds-entire-1-billion-bitcoin-buy-with-hybrid-securities</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普相关的世界自由项目面临投资者的反抗</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-12/trump-linked-world-liberty-crypto-project-faces-investor-revolt</link><description>特朗普家族的加密货币企业世界自由金融公司 (World Liberty Financial Inc.) 正面临投资者的反抗，其中包括亿万富翁支持者贾斯汀·孙 (Justin Sun)，他指责该项目秘密建立控制措施，让内部人士冻结代币持有者的资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iu_BwazV59dw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 23:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-12/trump-linked-world-liberty-crypto-project-faces-investor-revolt</guid></item></channel></rss>